'''''Turkish Odyssey, A Cultural Guide to Turkey''''' is a guidebook written by [[≈ûerif Yenen]], it is the ‚Äúfirst guidebook of Turkey ever written by a Turk‚Äù.<ref name="traveler">{{cite news | first = | last = | authorlink = | author = | title= Gezginlerin kitabƒ± |trans-title=The Travelers' Book | url = http://hurarsiv.hurriyet.com.tr/goster/ShowNew.aspx?id=-37208 | format= | newspaper = [[H√ºrriyet]] |date= 7 September 1998 |accessdate= 27 March 2012 |language=tr}}</ref><ref name="Rehberler">{{cite news | first = Hasan | last = Tuzluoƒülu | authorlink = | title= Seyahat: Turistin b√ºy√ºkel√ßisi rehberler |trans-title=Travel: Guides, ambassadors of tourists | url =http://www.hurriyet.com.tr/seyahat/3958295_p.asp | format= | newspaper = [[H√ºrriyet]] |date= 20 February 2006 |accessdate= 27 March 2012 |language=tr}}</ref> The book was first published in English in September 1998, the version with a CD-ROM was in 2001, the fourth edition was in 2007. It is translated into Italian, Turkish and German. It is used as textbook and is on suggested reading lists at various universities.<ref name="ozdal">{{Cite web |url =http://w3.gazi.edu.tr/~ozdald |title =Gazi University Turizm ƒ∞≈ületme ve Turist Rehberliƒüi Anabilim Dalƒ± |accessdate= 27 March 2012 | last = Deƒüirmencioƒülu | first =Yrd. Do√ß. Dr. A. √ñzdal |date= | publisher =[[Gazi University]] |language=tr}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url =http://www.balikesir.edu.tr/~bologna/tr/btioyo/turist/mesleki_yabanci_dil3.doc |title =Lisans Programƒ± Ders Tanƒ±tƒ±m Formu |accessdate =27 March 2012 |last = |first = |date = |publisher =Balƒ±kesir University Turizm ƒ∞≈ületme ve Turist Rehberliƒüi B√∂l√ºm√º |language =tr |deadurl =yes |archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20120511101406/http://www.balikesir.edu.tr/~bologna/tr/btioyo/turist/mesleki_yabanci_dil3.doc |archivedate =11 May 2012 |df = }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url =http://files.tulga1.webnode.com.tr/200000015-84637855ea/cografyakapsam.pdf |title =Ba≈ükent University,