'''WordReference''' is an [[online]] [[translation dictionary]] for, among others, the language pairs [[English language|English]]-[[French language|French]], English-[[Italian language|Italian]], English-[[Spanish language|Spanish]], French-Spanish, Spanish-[[Portuguese language|Portuguese]] and English-Portuguese. 

WordReference also has Oxford Unabridged and Concise dictionaries available for a subscription. These dictionaries contain more translations than the free ones. The price is currently 30EUR (45USD) per year.<ref>{{cite web | year=2009 | url = http://www.wordreference.com/english/Oxford-subscriptions.aspx | title = WordReference Subscription Dictionaries | accessdate = 2009-02-16 }}</ref>

As of June 2008, more language pairs have been created: English-[[German language|German]], English-[[Russian language|Russian]], English-[[Polish language|Polish]], English-[[Romanian language|Romanian]], English-[[Czech language|Czech]], English-[[Greek language|Greek]], English-[[Turkish language|Turkish]], English-[[Chinese language|Chinese]], English-[[Japanese language|Japanese]], English-[[Korean language|Korean]], English-[[Arabic language|Arabic]]. Presently the newer additions are still works-in-progress.

According to [[Alexa.com]],<ref>[http://www.alexa.com/data/details/main/wordreference.com wordreference.com - Site Information from Alexa<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> the website is one of the 500 most visited websites worldwide.

